name: Grace Smith
description: Well, looking at my pictures you can see I am really different. I am sexy, attractive, independent and strong, but there is a little angel inside of me too that wants to be protected by her man. I am a very direct person, I definitely know what I want and I always do what I say. I am honest and reliable. My friends can trust me and know that I will always help them when they need me. I am passionate about everything I do, well, a real latin girl. I am really strong. But don’t be afraid. My leg is strong enough for a good kick, but you will melt from my tender kiss one day too
